Class NonExtractableComponentException

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class NonExtractableComponentException
extends IAIKPkcs11Exception
    This exception signals that there was an attempt to retrieve a key component which cannot be extracted from the token.

    A typical cause is if the application tries to extract the private exponent of a RSA private key or the key material of a secret key.

    Author:
    Karl Scheibelhofer
